question: ETH above $1,750 on May 13?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the Binance 1 minute candle for ETH/USDT titled 2023/05/13 12:00 in the ET timezone (referring to noon ET) has a final “Close” price of 1,750.01 or higher, or to "No" otherwise.

The resolution source for this market is https://www.binance.com, specifically the ETH/USDT “Close” prices, currently available at https://www.binance.com/en/trade/ETH_USDT. The Binance API url for ETH/USDT may be used in the event that the chart is unavailable.

Please note that this market is about the price according to Binance ETH/USDT, not according to other sources or spot markets.

question: Will Galatasaray win the 2022–23 Turkish Süper Lig?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Galatasaray (Galatasaray Spor Kulübü) wins the 2022–23 Süper Lig. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If this team is eliminated from contention to be champion of the 2022–23 Süper Lig or it otherwise becomes impossible for this team to win due to league rules, this market may immediately resolve to "No".

If the 2022–23 Süper Lig champion is not decided by November 31, 2023, the market will resolve to 50-50.

events.title: Turkish Süper Lig Champion
events.description: This is a market group over which team will win champion of the Spor Toto Süper Lig 2022–23 season.
